languages.text: "Здесь так просторно! Небо над головой просто огромно. И под ногами еще сотни и сотни шпилей... Так вот каков дворец Вольного Торговца!"
"It's absolutely vast! The sky above seems to stretch on and on. And all the spires below — hundreds and hundreds of them... So this is the Rogue Trader's palace!"

languages.text: “它真的非常庞大！上面的天空似乎在不断延伸，而下面所有的尖塔——有成百上千座尖塔……原来行商浪人的宫殿是这个样子！”
languages.original_text: "It's absolutely vast! The sky above seems to stretch on and on. And all the spires below — hundreds and hundreds of them... So this is the Rogue Trader's palace!"

traits.speaker: CassiaCompanion

languages.text: «¡Es increíblemente inmenso! El cielo parece continuar sin fin. Y todas las torres a nuestros pies, cientos y cientos de ellas... ¡De modo que este es el palacio de{mf|l| la} Comerciante Independiente!».

traits.speaker: CassiaCompanion

languages.text: 「なんと広大な！空がどこまでも続いているかのようだ。そして、眼下には何百もの尖塔が…では、ここが自由開拓者（ローグトレーダー）の宮殿なのか！」
languages.original_text: "It's absolutely vast! The sky above seems to stretch on and on. And all the spires below — hundreds and hundreds of them... So this is the Rogue Trader's palace!"

languages.text: "Ist das groß! Der Himmel scheint endlos zu sein. Und all die Türme darunter ... Hunderte und Aberhunderte ... Das ist also der Palast {mf|des Freihändlers|der Freihändlerin}!"
languages.original_text: "It's absolutely vast! The sky above seems to stretch on and on. And all the spires below — hundreds and hundreds of them... So this is the Rogue Trader's palace!"

languages.text: « L'endroit est gigantesque ! Les cieux semblent s'étirer à l'infini. Et toutes ces tours... Il y en a des centaines... Voilà donc le palais {mf|du libre-marchand|de la libre-marchande} ! »
